{
  "id": "69febb5689a5007a2976bea3",
  "title": "法曹界内の「強さ」は分かるものなのだろうか",
  "created": 1778301783,
  "updated": 1778301800,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69febb5689a5007a2976bea3",
      "text": "法曹界内の「強さ」は分かるものなのだろうか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb42e",
      "text": "from [任天堂法務部は別に最強ではない]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb42f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301787
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb430",
      "text": "[法曹界内の「強さ」は分かるものなのだろうか]……。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb431",
      "text": "\tあるいは、[法曹界内の「強さ」]の話として最強が使われているのだろうか。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb432",
      "text": " \t[法曹界内の「強さ」]で言えば[任天堂]みたいな企業の[法務部]ではなく、[国家機関]が最強だと思う。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb433",
      "text": " \t\t[hoagecko.icon]は[最高裁]だと思います[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb434",
      "text": " \t\t\t前にも[最高裁判所]のページに書いた通りです",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb435",
      "text": " \t\t\t流石に内容が「最高裁判所」のページタイトルらしくないので切り出してみた。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb436",
      "text": "  \t\t\t→ [以下、日本の最高裁・司法の主だった業績を書いてみます]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb437",
      "text": "  \t\t\t\t忘れてました。ありがと[hoagecko.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb438",
      "text": "  \t次点で[在日米軍]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb439",
      "text": "  \t\t公務中の事件だったら[第一次裁判権]がなかったりとかなり強い",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb43a",
      "text": "  \t\t\t\t[https://ja.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%9C%A8%E6%97%A5%E7%B1%B3%E8%BB%8D%E8%A3%81%E5%88%A4%E6%A8%A9%E6%94%BE%E6%A3%84%E5%AF%86%E7%B4%84%E4%BA%8B%E4%BB%B6 在日米軍裁判権放棄密約事件 - Wikipedia]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb43b",
      "text": "  \t\t\tそもそも弁護士の出番がないから別枠感がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb43c",
      "text": "  \t\t\t\tある意味[チート]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb43d",
      "text": "  \t\t\t場合によっちゃ[最高裁]よりも強いかも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb43e",
      "text": "  \t\t\t\t我が国の主権とは……[とはちゃん.icon][Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb43f",
      "text": "  \tあとは現職の[国会議員]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb440",
      "text": "  \t\t[不逮捕特権]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb441",
      "text": "  \t\t\tこれはそもそも裁判が始まらないだけだから違うか",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb442",
      "text": "  \t\t\t\t少なくとも辞めない限り時間稼ぎができるという意味ではやっぱり強いかも",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb443",
      "text": "  \t\t\t[ガーシー]の場合だと弾劾後普通に即捕まっていたし",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb444",
      "text": "\t\t\t[草.icon]。それはそう。[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301783
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb445",
      "text": "\t私（[Summer498.icon]）は[ゲーム業界]や[エンタメ]の[知財]の[法務部]の中で最強とかくらいに読んでた。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301783,
      "updated": 1778301800
    },
    {
      "id": "69febb560000000000dfb446",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778301800,
      "updated": 1778301800
